<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>New Reply: {{discussionTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #17a2b8 0%, #138496 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .reply-box {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #17a2b8;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>New Reply</h1>
        <p>{{courseName}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{recipientName}},</h2>
        
        <p>A new reply has been added to the discussion <strong>{{discussionTitle}}</strong> in your course <strong>{{courseName}}</strong>.</p>
        
        <div class="reply-box">
            <h3>{{discussionTitle}}</h3>
            <p><strong>Replied by:</strong> {{authorName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{notificationDate}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Join the conversation and continue the discussion!</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{discussionUrl}}" class="button">View Reply</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>Stay engaged with your learning community by participating in discussions.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The E-Learning Platform Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to you because you're enrolled in this course.</p>
        <p>Â© 2025 E-Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 